ExternalData.Subtitlesect: International Coffee Agreement, 1968, as extended with modifications by the International Coffee Council in Resolution No. 264 of 14 April 1973*
ExternalData.EIF: 1 October 1973. The Agreement was extended on 1 October 1975 by the Protocol for the Continuation in Force of the International Coffee Agreement 1968, as extended [see chapter XIX.5 c)].
